headline: 3 Brilliant Dividend Stocks to Buy Now and Hold for the Long Term
summary: Prologis has grown its dividend at a 13% compound annual rate over the past five years.  Realty Income has increased its monthly dividend payment 131 times since its public market listing in 1994.  Mid-America Apartment Communities has grown its dividend at a 7% compound annual rate over the last decade.
